dmca.title: Subpoena Report
dmca.body:
SBC Internet Services
Legal Department
1010 N. St. Mary's ST., 14th Flr.
San Antonio, Texas 78215
Phone: 210.246.8696
Fax: 210.246.8699

Subpoena issued by United States District Court Northern District of California

SBC has been commanded to produce and permit inspection and copying of the following documents or objects at the place, date, and time specified below(12-21-2005).(list of documents or objects): Information, including name, address, telephone number, e-mail address, and Media Access Control addresses, sufficient to identify the alleged infringers of copyrighted sound recordings, listed by IP addrss in attachment A to this Subpoena.
